{"tid":2322090,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"美國紅藍兩黨豪賭 攬炒全美國","createTime":"2020-12-12T05:02:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T05:55:43.000Z","uid":239510,"like":11,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"82319e2acf871f2acbf3131772eb8cca0e69953d","tid":2322090,"uid":239510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T05:02:20.000Z","msg":"件事發生到咁係有小小意料之外<br />\n<br />\n但正如連登仔所講 法院唔想孭鑊 但佢地可能將會因為咁而令美國分裂<br />\n<br />\n宜家最後既死線就得兩條<br />\n<br />\n第一條係德州公投啟動<br />\n第二條係公投支持獨來通過<br />\n如果呢個條線都過埋<br />\n隨時美國一分為二 可以預計到一啲深紅既州都可能會咁做<br />\n<br />\n如果兩條線都過曬 最高法院又否決德州既投票會係最差結果<br />\n<br />\n由公投出左支持個刻其實美國已經玩完<br />\n法院點玩 只係變和平分手定戰爭既局面<br />\n<br />\n無論點 最高法院一定會被歷史記住 遺息萬年<br />\n<br />\n可以話搞成咁其實都係有可能預見到 4年前侵上台其實就係紅藍既一次決鬥 <br />\n兩黨惡鬥一日唔解 美國遲早都會散 兩類價值觀完全唔同既人 遲早會意見不合<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nGOD bless U.S<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e50c27a1b43924b017a5c9de7c704aa1bb3fdf","tid":2322090,"uid":63,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T05:04:17.000Z","msg":"有無你講到咁誇張呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61634221fc35e176066697e0d8cae6d182ded526","tid":2322090,"uid":361751,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T05:05:03.000Z","msg":"笑咗<br />\n<br />\n你去過美國未"},{"pid":"51fa0a3f254776734ced01df96efe88ebbcbe867","tid":2322090,"uid":130105,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T05:05:06.000Z","msg":"其實點只兩黨，傳媒、big tech、正苦都要附上責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03df3a4915e2e2e2eea52e3a8d35afef5d9a4a09","tid":2322090,"uid":239510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"27e50c27a1b43924b017a5c9de7c704aa1bb3fdf","tid":2322090,"uid":63,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy